1. The font-size:

 <style>
            h2 { font-size: 200%; }
            p { font-size: 200%; }
        </style>

2. The font-weight:

 <style>
            h2 { font-weight: 800; }
            p { font-weight: 800; }
        </style>

3. The font-family:

 <style>
            h2 { font-family: Serif; }
            p { font-family: monospace; }
        </style>

4. The font-style:

 <style>
            h2 { font-style: italic; }
            p { font-style: italic; }
        </style>

5. The font-variant:

 <style>
            h2 { font-variant: small-caps; }
            p { font-variant: small-caps; }
        </style>

6. The font:

 <style>
            h2 { font: 20px arial bold 15px, sans-serif; }
            p { font: 15px arial, sans-serif; }
        </style>

Change the styles below:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Fonts Application</title>
        <style>
            h2 { font: 20px arial bold 15px, sans-serif; }
            p { font: 15px arial, sans-serif; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h2>The CSS Application Tutorial</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Software Developer tube channel, We look at the how CSS is used to style webpage.</p>
        <p>Welcome to Software Developer tube channel, We look at the how CSS is used to style webpage.</p>
